<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">啊 御前崎 在这断崖前
将海一分为二的
骏河之光 与远江之风
丸山薰</font>

1
00:00:25,017 --> 00:00:26,887
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">大海啊</font>

2
00:00:28,157 --> 00:00:31,777
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不 要忍住 不能叫</font>

3
00:00:33,957 --> 00:00:36,687
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">真好啊 大海</font>

4
00:00:38,727 --> 00:00:39,537
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">风景真不错</font>

5
00:00:44,997 --> 00:00:48,797
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">来这的路上拍的大海 得有五十张了</font>

6
00:00:50,157 --> 00:00:52,107
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这就是没有海的县民的天性吧</font>

7
00:01:00,517 --> 00:01:02,447
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">有狗爪印</font>

8
00:01:06,417 --> 00:01:07,497
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">狗狗好强</font>

9
00:01:09,807 --> 00:01:13,257
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">接下来要去妈妈拜托的挂川茶屋</font>

10
00:01:17,407 --> 00:01:19,607
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这次有好好做计划</font>

11
00:01:20,227 --> 00:01:21,907
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不会再有上次那样的失态了</font>

12
00:01:23,727 --> 00:01:24,277
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">大概</font>

13
00:01:26,677 --> 00:01:29,467
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">在海边骑车好爽啊</font>

14
00:01:31,037 --> 00:01:35,737
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">但是 风好大 好冷啊</font>

15
00:01:46,857 --> 00:01:54,247
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">摇曳露营 第二季</font>

16
00:03:09,137 --> 00:03:10,310
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">第2集 岁末的单人露营女孩</font>

17
00:03:10,347 --> 00:03:11,097
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">茶</font>

18
00:03:12,297 --> 00:03:15,787
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">实在是太多了 不知道选哪个好</font>

19
00:03:16,897 --> 00:03:20,857
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你好 请问能不能推荐一下2千日元左右的茶</font>

20
00:03:21,187 --> 00:03:22,267
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这个嘛</font>

21
00:03:22,887 --> 00:03:25,947
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那么 这个“秘藏”怎么样呢</font>

22
00:03:27,507 --> 00:03:30,587
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这是在深山窖藏一夏的发酵茶</font>

23
00:03:31,797 --> 00:03:34,897
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">去掉了刺激的味道 十分温和</font>

24
00:03:36,557 --> 00:03:38,467
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">虽然不太懂 但是好好喝</font>

25
00:03:40,707 --> 00:03:44,667
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你是不是 我在夜叉神岭碰到的小姑娘呀</font>

26
00:03:51,837 --> 00:03:52,707
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是那个时候的</font>

27
00:03:53,027 --> 00:03:53,637
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你好</font>

28
00:03:54,297 --> 00:03:58,657
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">谢谢你之前送的焙茶 非常好喝</font>

29
00:03:59,027 --> 00:04:01,677
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不客气 真是太巧了呢</font>

30
00:04:02,437 --> 00:04:04,367
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你今天一个人来挂川的吗</font>

31
00:04:04,517 --> 00:04:08,077
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是的 我要去磐田海边看新年日出</font>

32
00:04:09,197 --> 00:04:11,087
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">所以才大老远从山梨过来了啊</font>

33
00:04:12,107 --> 00:04:15,387
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">要去磐田的话 福田海岸应该不错</font>

34
00:04:15,767 --> 00:04:17,917
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">福田海岸吗</font>

35
00:04:18,187 --> 00:04:22,157
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是的 那附近是有名的新年日出景点</font>

36
00:04:22,497 --> 00:04:27,827
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">到了岁末还会在海边搭起鸟居 氛围很奇妙</font>

37
00:04:29,367 --> 00:04:30,957
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那我去那看看</font>

38
00:04:32,347 --> 00:04:34,987
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">路上小心 欢迎你再来</font>

39
00:04:35,297 --> 00:04:35,997
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好的</font>

40
00:04:37,647 --> 00:04:39,467
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我刚在茶屋买好茶了</font>

41
00:04:40,027 --> 00:04:41,107
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">辛苦了</font>

42
00:04:41,767 --> 00:04:45,967
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那家店的二楼是绿茶咖啡厅 去歇歇脚吧</font>

43
00:04:47,607 --> 00:04:49,327
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我多给了你1000日元吧</font>

44
00:04:50,297 --> 00:04:50,947
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">真的假的</font>

45
00:04:51,787 --> 00:04:54,057
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">哎呀 这么快又来光顾啦</font>

46
00:04:54,137 --> 00:04:55,547
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">你 你好</font>

47
00:04:58,257 --> 00:04:59,927
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">真的有咖啡厅啊</font>

48
00:05:01,257 --> 00:05:04,357
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">久等了 这是抹茶提拉米苏和绿茶套餐</font>

49
00:05:05,207 --> 00:05:06,407
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那我开动了</font>

50
00:05:16,987 --> 00:05:19,687
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这个茶点套餐 异常地让人感到安定</font>

51
00:05:20,507 --> 00:05:22,477
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">让人想起了驹根的温泉</font>

52
00:05:23,737 --> 00:05:25,997
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我知道了 这个叫做能喝的“泡汤”</font>

53
00:05:26,877 --> 00:05:29,587
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不行了 不想动了</font>

54
00:05:30,527 --> 00:05:31,977
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好想在这里搭帐篷</font>

55
00:05:37,007 --> 00:05:38,527
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">下路的寄送完成了</font>

56
00:05:44,507 --> 00:05:46,207
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">怎么有一片黑云呢</font>

57
00:05:51,117 --> 00:05:53,167
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">到达见付天神神社</font>

58
00:05:54,247 --> 00:05:55,457
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">很顺利</font>

59
00:05:56,277 --> 00:05:59,997
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">提前算好停留时间和移动时间是正确的</font>

60
00:06:06,057 --> 00:06:07,697
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这就是悉平太郎啊</font>

61
00:06:08,507 --> 00:06:11,777
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">比光前寺的早太郎看起来更像狐狸</font>

62
00:06:14,197 --> 00:06:17,447
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不愧是岁末日 没什么人啊</font>

63
00:06:20,897 --> 00:06:23,187
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是牛
（许愿牛（雌））</font>

64
00:06:25,437 --> 00:06:26,907
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">年末最后的参拜</font>

65
00:06:27,887 --> 00:06:31,607
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">希望明年也能安安稳稳</font>

66
00:06:32,637 --> 00:06:33,167
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好了</font>

67
00:06:34,477 --> 00:06:36,117
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">去看活的悉平太郎了</font>

68
00:06:38,387 --> 00:06:38,957
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">请问</font>

69
00:06:40,057 --> 00:06:43,697
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我听说这里养着悉平太郎三世
(悉平护符 抽签 见付天神)</font>

70
00:06:45,687 --> 00:06:47,537
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">其实它几年前就</font>

71
00:06:51,937 --> 00:06:55,567
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">仔细想想 狗狗的寿命也就15年左右</font>

72
00:06:56,977 --> 00:06:59,217
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">比人类要短得多啊</font>

73
00:07:01,797 --> 00:07:06,177
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我来找见付天神的悉平三世 但是它已经去世了</font>

74
00:07:07,167 --> 00:07:09,457
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这样啊 真遗憾</font>

75
00:07:10,337 --> 00:07:12,647
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">然后我就想到</font>

76
00:07:13,467 --> 00:07:18,827
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">狗的寿命比人类短得多 不能一起生活数十年的吧</font>

77
00:07:19,817 --> 00:07:22,877
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">斋藤不害怕和竹轮分开吗</font>

78
00:07:24,737 --> 00:07:28,187
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">当然很害怕 而且会很悲伤</font>

79
00:07:29,137 --> 00:07:30,377
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">但那也是没办法的事</font>

80
00:07:31,497 --> 00:07:36,197
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">所以 现在就要好好陪它玩 让它开开心心的</font>

81
00:07:37,317 --> 00:07:38,017
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这样啊</font>

82
00:07:38,777 --> 00:07:41,317
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对了 从圣诞露营回来</font>

83
00:07:41,387 --> 00:07:44,877
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我给竹轮看了大家的合照 它特别开心哦</font>

84
00:07:46,097 --> 00:07:46,847
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这样啊</font>

85
00:07:48,787 --> 00:07:50,437
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">还要再一起玩哦 小凛</font>

86
00:07:51,807 --> 00:07:54,657
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 接下来要好好陪它玩个痛快</font>

87
00:07:55,927 --> 00:07:56,837
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">感谢惠顾</font>

88
00:07:58,317 --> 00:08:01,277
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">悉平太郎的狗狗签 到手</font>

89
00:08:02,987 --> 00:08:04,667
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">差不多该去露营地了</font>

90
00:08:06,997 --> 00:08:07,697
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是大吉</font>

91
00:08:10,007 --> 00:08:12,207
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">自由营地 过夜到明天对吧</font>

92
00:08:12,637 --> 00:08:13,217
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是的</font>

93
00:08:17,327 --> 00:08:19,697
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那前面就是海吗</font>

94
00:08:22,487 --> 00:08:24,157
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">赶快搭好帐篷</font>

95
00:08:25,337 --> 00:08:26,847
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 去看海</font>

96
00:08:27,737 --> 00:08:31,787
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">镭温泉 光明石大浴场
救助号 乘船点</font>

97
00:08:37,137 --> 00:08:38,827
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这里也有灯台啊</font>

98
00:08:47,857 --> 00:08:48,417
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">富士山</font>

99
00:08:49,447 --> 00:08:52,357
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">虽然很小 不过真的连这里都能看见呢</font>

100
00:09:03,837 --> 00:09:05,277
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">太阳也要落山了</font>

101
00:09:06,457 --> 00:09:08,107
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">开始生火吧</font>

102
00:09:09,467 --> 00:09:12,127
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">不过 整备妥当的露营地</font>

103
00:09:12,677 --> 00:09:14,907
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">就没有松子球和树枝捡了啊</font>

104
00:09:16,357 --> 00:09:18,257
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那就用柴花来引火</font>

105
00:09:18,637 --> 00:09:20,657
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">柴花
(柴花（Feather stick）)</font>

106
00:09:20,667 --> 00:09:24,677
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">将劈成细条的木柴表面用小刀削成羽毛状</font>

107
00:09:24,747 --> 00:09:27,243
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">使其更便于引燃的加工法</font>

108
00:09:27,757 --> 00:09:28,577
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">就这样吧</font>

109
00:09:29,457 --> 00:09:31,507
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">接下来就用炉子烧水</font>

110
00:09:32,797 --> 00:09:35,127
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这个看起来好像彼岸花啊</font>

111
00:09:39,597 --> 00:09:43,127
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">这么好点着 都不用助燃物了</font>

112
00:09:44,057 --> 00:09:45,447
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">永别了 松子球</font>

113
00:09:45,957 --> 00:09:46,867
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">等一下啦</font>

114
00:09:48,117 --> 00:09:49,107
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">好 水开了</font>

115
00:09:50,767 --> 00:09:52,917
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">跨年荞麦面就用这个轻松完成
(地道做法 含家鸭浓汤 速食袋装面
鸭肉高汤荞麦面)</font>

116
00:09:53,687 --> 00:09:55,977
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">把滑菇和荞麦面一起煮</font>

117
00:09:56,297 --> 00:09:59,177
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">再加上葱 海苔 炸白身鱼和鸡蛋</font>

118
00:09:59,577 --> 00:10:01,387
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">撒上大量七味粉</font>

119
00:10:03,557 --> 00:10:04,817
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">鸭汤滑菇荞麦面</font>

120
00:10:06,797 --> 00:10:09,987
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">光是装在碗里 就有过年的感觉了</font>

121
00:10:11,687 --> 00:10:12,617
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我开动了</font>

122
00:10:26,047 --> 00:10:30,047
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">果然冬天的露营美食 就是少不了辣口的汤水啊</font>

123
00:10:31,267 --> 00:10:34,027
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对了 忘记传照片了</font>

124
00:10:35,427 --> 00:10:37,777
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我把年末单人露营的照片上传了</font>

125
00:10:39,167 --> 00:10:40,087
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是大海耶</font>

126
00:10:40,747 --> 00:10:42,827
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小凛 大海的照片也拍太多张了吧</font>

127
00:10:43,267 --> 00:10:43,917
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">秒回啊</font>

128
00:10:44,767 --> 00:10:48,357
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">向往大海 是山梨人的天性哦 抚子</font>

129
00:10:48,607 --> 00:10:52,507
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">就是呀 抚子不也拍了好多张富士山嘛</font>

130
00:10:52,677 --> 00:10:54,197
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">有理有据 无法反驳</font>

131
00:10:54,457 --> 00:10:56,317
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">大家新年好呀</font>

132
00:10:56,387 --> 00:10:57,217
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">还早着呢</font>

133
00:10:57,297 --> 00:10:59,867
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">压岁钱就用“拿马逊”礼券代替吧</font>

134
00:11:00,297 --> 00:11:03,387
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">那我给你送2万日元份 都是用过的</font>

135
00:11:04,837 --> 00:11:07,917
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">对了 我们这边下雪了哦 下雪了</font>

136
00:11:08,127 --> 00:11:08,947
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">是吗</font>

137
00:11:10,457 --> 00:11:14,387
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">滨松从来不下雪 我现在可开心了</font>

138
00:11:17,907 --> 00:11:21,427
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">因为那家伙 今年下半年过得特别热闹</font>

139
00:11:23,087 --> 00:11:25,257
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">往年露营都只到1月份</font>

140
00:11:26,247 --> 00:11:29,097
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">明年暖和起来应该也还会继续露营吧</font>

141
00:11:30,797 --> 00:11:31,967
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">而且也考上驾照了</font>

142
00:11:33,997 --> 00:11:36,227
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小凛 过年好呀</font>

143
00:11:36,307 --> 00:11:38,467
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">嗯 过年好</font>

144
00:11:53,407 --> 00:11:56,427
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">早呀 犬子 新年好</font>

145
00:11:57,377 --> 00:11:59,257
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">新年好呀</font>

146
00:11:59,987 --> 00:12:01,527
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">真是好冷呀</font>

147
00:12:02,047 --> 00:12:03,507
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">老师 新年好</font>

148
00:12:03,947 --> 00:12:05,727
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">新年好 大垣同学</font>

149
00:12:06,967 --> 00:12:08,967
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">还麻烦您开车出来 太感谢啦</font>

150
00:12:09,487 --> 00:12:12,547
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">反正我也没什么事 不客气</font>

151
00:12:13,917 --> 00:12:16,537
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小明 要看过新年日出再去打工吗</font>

152
00:12:16,767 --> 00:12:19,447
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">嗯 犬子马上要去高山了吗</font>

153
00:12:19,657 --> 00:12:20,647
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">中午再去</font>

154
00:12:22,197 --> 00:12:23,517
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">雪球</font>

155
00:12:23,697 --> 00:12:24,297
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小明</font>

156
00:12:24,617 --> 00:12:25,807
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">新年快乐</font>

157
00:12:27,597 --> 00:12:29,097
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小 小犬子</font>

158
00:12:29,657 --> 00:12:33,387
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">我说我要去看新年日出 她就说也想去</font>

159
00:12:33,827 --> 00:12:35,447
<font color="#FFFFFF" size="16">小明 压岁钱拿来</font>

